                skos:editorialNote "DIN audit fix (2026-06-09): DIN EN ISO 4885 §3.200 lemma is 'Randschichthärten'; DIN 17022-5 uses 'Randschichthärten' exclusively in its title. The hto-edit.owl DE label 'Oberflächenhärtung' is a DIN-10052 / legacy synonym (already retained in hto-edit.owl as skos:altLabel — preserved here). The DIN-canonical 'Randschichthärten' is hoisted to skos:prefLabel."@en .


